// - Combinatorics: factorial_i32/f64, binomial_i32
// - Interpolation: lerp, inverse_lerp, map_range, smoothstep, smootherstep
// - Range: clamp, wrap, ping_pong
// - Conversion: deg_to_rad, rad_to_deg
